# Client half (`client/`)

When working in `client/`, read and follow:

@client/CLAUDE.md

For TipTap/Fabric editor internals, also read:

@client/src/components/README.md

## Quick reminders

- Stack: React 19 + TypeScript + Vite + Tailwind v4 + shadcn/ui + Zustand.
- API calls via `client/src/lib/axios.ts` (`VITE_API_URL`, JWT Bearer on every request).
- Deploy target: Vercel.
- Run tests: `cd client && npm test` and `cd client && npm run lint`.
- Git commands only inside `client/` — it is its own repo.
